description:
Comment: Version 2: 22 pages, 11 figures. More figures added, additional cases
  discussed. Misprints corrected. Keywords: Maxwell fisheye, Eaton lens;
  Non-Euclidean geometry; Stereographic projection; Transformation optics;
  Metamaterials; Perfect lens. The last version appears at J. Modern Opt. 57
  (2010), no. 7, 511-527

  By integrating a series provided by Knopp, a series representation of the
Euler-Mascheroni constant arises. The infinite sum representation of {\gamma}
is determined through Fourier series (sawtooth wave).
